{"tid":707060,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"克羅地亞卡連歷被逐出國家隊","createTime":"2018-06-18T11:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T15:31:00.000Z","uid":55981,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"1aabf3bbc1ffe88e7cdf2c8770f4f5416b7f39e1","tid":707060,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:31:50.000Z","msg":"克羅地亞射手卡連歷因為上場拒絕後備入替，在周一被逐出國家隊。<br />\n<br />\n克羅地亞在首場世界盃D組旗開得勝，以2:0擊敗尼日利亞；在這場勝仗，教練達歷在餘下5分鐘時，欲換出卡連歷（Nikola Kalinic），讓正選射手文迪蘇傑提早休息，但已經連續4場任後備的卡連歷，以背痛為理由拒絕上陣，最終由另一鋒將比真卡入替。 據報，達歷並不相信卡連歷有傷，因此兩人爆發矛盾，更於周一把後者驅逐出國家隊，在今次世界盃決賽周都不會再起用對方。 30歲的卡連歷自從2008年入選克羅地亞後，上陣41場攻入15球；早年於費倫天拿上位後，在去年夏天以2500萬歐元加盟AC米蘭，可是未能保持高入球率，未能穩佔正選席位，整季上陣41場僅入6球。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://更多now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9Anow.com&d=nvueCfnSCfy7NfZdOypNw7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=58c24b83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">更多now.com</a>體育新聞及英超、西甲精華，請按此"},{"pid":"93959ad08ca424bd55c95b4da655d982a41faf3c","tid":707060,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/croatia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b0ca04f7e9e4ab8ba11a8600765662bba3680e","tid":707060,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef339d8641653a81481443862cbff24218fa2f6","tid":707060,"uid":52006,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"以為自己好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe7f43fb86caddf63d7699f5781a9e4b7360708","tid":707060,"uid":30319,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"選佢已經係錯"},{"pid":"69498cbe12b3da9d335651cd6554684d80f403c7","tid":707060,"uid":6297,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"repl